msgid "Semantic Analysis"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Csemantic-analysis.md:3
msgid ""
"The Semantic Analysis tab in the Chain Builder helps you understand how DMN "
"variables from different government agencies relate to each other through "
"shared SKOS concepts, and why some chains execute sequentially rather than "
"as unified DRDs."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Csemantic-analysis.md:7
msgid "Opening the Semantic Analysis tab"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Csemantic-analysis.md:9
msgid ""
"In the Chain Builder, click the **Semantic Analysis** tab header above the "
"Chain Composer. The tab loads automatically from the active TriplyDB "
"endpoint."
msgstr ""

